; Coverage test for value.cc lines 706-721
; Exercise amount /= balance path where balance simplifies to single amount
; This happens when dividing a commodity amount by a total amount
; that is represented as a balance but has only one commodity

commodity $
commodity AAPL

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $50.00
P 2024/06/01 AAPL $60.00

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage      10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash            $-500.00

; When using -V, amounts get converted and divisions may happen
test reg Assets:Brokerage -V
24-Jan-01 Buy Stock             Assets:Brokerage            $500.00      $500.00
24-Jun-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $100.00      $600.00
end test
